  <thing id="xRvnFinRst" name="Final Rest" description="You can grant [i}final rest{/i} by tracing your deity&#146;s symbol on a newly dead body. That corpse then receives a Will save (using your Will save bonus) to resist any attempt to transform it into an undead creature, including animate dead and create undead spells and the create spawn ability of undead creatures. This is a spell-like ability us can use once per day." compset="Special" summary="Grant a corpse the ability to resist becoming undead.">
