  <thing id="fRvnReinca" name="Reincarnated" description="You have vague, dreamlike memories of a former life. You even possess skills you&apos;ve never knowingly learned.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: Choose a nonrestricted skill you do not have as a class skill. That skill is always considered a class skill for you. Your spirit was reborn because it is emotionally linked to a creature that has lingered in this world. If you ever encounter your &quot;soul mate,&quot; it will instinctually recognize you, and you gain a +2 bonus to all Charisma-based skill checks when interacting with it.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: You may take this feat only at the beginning of the game." compset="Feat" summary="You enjoy a +4 bonus to all Madness saves." uniqueness="useronce">
