  <thing id="gBookBlank" name="Book, Blank" description="These books are smaller and less durably bound than a wizard&apos;s sturdy spellbook. A typical book measures 4 by 6 inches and has one hundred pages of parchment. Books of this quality are often used for personal journals or published works." compset="Gear">
